'''Dave Thomas''' is a physicist and mathematician, mostly known for his writings and research on the [[paranormal]] (such as [[UFO]] sightings in [[Roswell, New Mexico|Roswell]], [[New Mexico]] and Aztec, New Mexico, as well as finding codings in other texts that dispute the credibility of the [[Bible Code]]).

Thomas is a graduate of the [[New Mexico Institute of Mining and Technology]], with a bachelor's degree in mathematics and physics and a masters degree in mathematics. He is known for his work [http://www.nmsr.org/biblecod.htm debunking] the [[Bible code]].

Thomas is currently president of [http://www.nmsr.org New Mexicans for Science and Reason] and a past president of the [http://www.nmas.org New Mexico Academy of Science], and is also a Fellow of the [[Committee for Skeptical Inquiry]].

